Ing '''Amanung Cornish''' (king Cornish, ''Kernewek/Kernowek'' king [[Cornish language#Standard Written Form (SWF)|Standard Written Form]]; misusulat ya muring ''Kernewek'' king [[Cornish language#Unified Cornish (UC)|UC]] ampong [[Cornish language#Kernewek Kemmyn o Common Cornish (KK)|KK]], ''Kernowek'' king [[Cornish language#Unified Cornish Revised (UCR)|UCR]], ''Curnoack'' king [[Cornish language#Modern Cornish o Revived Late Cornish (RLC)|RLC]]) metung ya kareng grupu da reng amanung ausan dang [[Brythonic]], a sanga da naman deng amanung [[w:Celtic languages|Celtic]]. Gagamitan de iti king [[Cornwall]]. Migsilbi yang amanung balen ing Cornish angga kanitang kalabingwalung (18) siglu o dilanua, at biniayan deng pasibayu aniang umpisa ning kaduangpulung (20) siglu.   

